  anyway, new version (#27053) that contains a bug fix,
  update submitted by B. K. Oxley (binkley) <binkley@alumni.rice.edu>
  and cleaned-up by Chris Bainbridge chrb@dcs.ed.ac.uk

*boost-1.30.0 (16 May 2003)

